Document: PhysicsDirectSpaceState2D
Path: godot/classes/class_physicsdirectspacestate2d.rst
Summary: Provides direct access to a physics space in the PhysicsServer2D, primarily for performing queries against objects and areas.

Note: This class is not meant to be instantiated directly. Use World2D.direct_space_state to get the world's physics 2D space state.
